### 获取驾驶舱核心统计
GET http://localhost:8080/api/dashboard/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 获取分类分布
GET http://localhost:8080/api/dashboard/category-distribution
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 获取部门金额排行
GET http://localhost:8080/api/dashboard/department-ranking
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 获取月度折旧趋势
GET http://localhost:8080/api/dashboard/depreciation-trend
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
